{"tid":2179594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大撕文宣 科大禁便條 理大遮黑紙  民主牆滿佈國安紅線 容不下一張白紙","createTime":"2020-08-29T08:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:52:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b59288f498b0b392576c43f7f878ebbd91a7f83d","tid":2179594,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/DQU47PWYB5A6XBOUYLKQMPOWWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FDQU47PWYB5A6XBOUYLKQMPOWWE%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=ee1f195b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FDQU47PWYB5A6XBOUYLKQMPOWWE%2F&h=988e6910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/DQU47PWYB5A6XBOUYLKQMPOWWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港大撕文宣 科大禁便條 理大遮黑紙 <br />\n民主牆滿佈國安紅線 容不下一張白紙<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國安法下紅線處處，代表言論自由的大學民主牆及連儂牆被校方「消毒」。香港大學被指撕走連儂牆的港獨文宣，學生會引述校方稱不希望「港獨」或「驅逐共黨」等標語再現牆上；科技大學更禁止同學在學生會告示板張貼無字便條。有大學學生會幹事坦言，大學乃至香港「已無任何自由表達嘅空間，就算唔講嘢都會犯法。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FJAmzozh7kgzXGmJWa2aBf7Z4gY=/2196x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T5OAECGK7FCGJF4Q3YSDEOGCPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFJAmzozh7kgzXGmJWa2aBf7Z4gY%3D%2F2196x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT5OAECGK7FCGJF4Q3YSDEOGCPI.jpg&h=c64a958b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【港大】■上月民主牆曾被校外人士撕毀，學生會及後重建，惟校方表明不希望有「港獨」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法實施前夕，6月底多間大學的民主牆及連儂牆先後遭人撕毀反修例文宣，包括港大。港大學生會會長葉芷琳指，上月11日深夜一批語帶鄉音的白衣人帶備工具到校拆除連儂牆，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會告示板也難逃一劫。科大學生會會長麥嘉俊表示，6月中五名校外人士深夜於北閘巴士站外，撕毀告示板上有關反修例。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n插手管理變相奪學生權力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u62bD__APCG1X8dM6_0jjKzwtHg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6I6DSL4D6VGDHHT2CTMPS27MYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu62bD__APCG1X8dM6_0jjKzwtHg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6I6DSL4D6VGDHHT2CTMPS27MYM.jpg&h=0f8b8b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【科大】■校方以避免衝突為由禁止張貼文宣，學生會會長麥嘉俊指空白便條紙亦遭撕走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RWE1l3yKkVu8sW22q30YTv7ztxw=/1836x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TMFEIKKOBNEWFGA3EE5SVHDACY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRWE1l3yKkVu8sW22q30YTv7ztxw%3D%2F1836x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTMFEIKKOBNEWFGA3EE5SVHDACY.jpg&h=f01b7c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【理大】■校方以黑紙遮蓋民主牆涉及港獨的字眼，學生會正副會長貼上空白便條抗議。<br />\n<br />\n「學校𠵱家係接受唔到任何文宣，連白紙都唔容許出現喺告示板上。」麥憶述爭議傳出後，有同學在學生會告示板貼空白便條紙抗議，。<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n麥指科大箝制言論自由向來甚於其他院校，大學本月8日便去信學生會，指學生會幹事未經批准下於校內舉辦多個活動，包。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於曾因民主牆風波而踢學生出校的理大，繼續干預由學生會管理的民主牆，包括以黑紙遮蓋民主牆上涉及港獨或其他敏感字眼；。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港已無自由表達空間」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kP8ro5wz49ZNO92rxQFlOMSQrLE=/3520x1688/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/37A5RRMOJBD2PNT6Y53FYKS6YY.GIF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkP8ro5wz49ZNO92rxQFlOMSQrLE%3D%2F3520x1688%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F37A5RRMOJBD2PNT6Y53FYKS6YY.GIF&h=b084bd17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理大學生會外務副會長鄭其浩表示，港版國安法條文含混，相信校園或連白紙文宣亦容不下，「呢度（香港）已經無任何畀你發揮自由同表達嘅空間，就算你唔講嘢都會犯法。」<br />\n<br />\n港大覆稱，上月11日晚，一批人士進入校園撕走大學街牆上的標貼，當保安人員趕至時，他們已離去。發言人稱，校。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n科大回覆指，已就佈告欄部份海報被人破壞一事報警，重申佈告欄僅適用於學生或大學舉辦的活動，用家須遵守使用守則。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"709ba7a8aeb60038d6428418784fb394db5afd93","tid":2179594,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8416545c9d001340fc0e22f828dec3c8ed5fe33c","tid":2179594,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c850b9919c437b4cba065b548915c766b13a50a6","tid":2179594,"uid":86745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"睇錯禁大便"},{"pid":"4f4474cbc422b8aa711cd3810b6b058507dbf896","tid":2179594,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c850b9919c437b4cba065b548915c766b13a50a6","tid":2179594,"uid":86745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"睇錯禁大便"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76540cd6e427acf7f42dcd507b3a05c164be08b2","tid":2179594,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}